#CAMERA 11
#phrase Deva  1
Tka-Rik... that was the name of a Magician in one of the fairy tales I heard in my childhood! That Magician sleeps in a cave on a remote island, and when he awakes the good times will return... but somehow I do not think the actual reality will be anything like the tale!
#ANIMATION 62
#CAMERA 2
#phrase Hero  2
Oh do not be so sure... mayhap they do have something in common. Tka-Rick does live in a cave in a remote land, and he does want to bring the good times back. That is why I am here - my mission was to find you.
