#ANIMATION 73
#CAMERA 3
#phrase Deva  8
Do not dare speak about At-Zako like that! We narrowly escaped the Curse of Joons together. You cannot imagine the horror of that...family and friends dead, one after the other, empty homes, bloody footprints in the dust of the road, and finally the Curse, the monster over which even your Great Magician would never be able to triumph.
#ANIMATION 73
